    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.cos((tmp + 0.78 * v2 + 0.50)))
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.82)) * (wp.exp(v0 + 0.50) - tmp))
    v0 = v0
    v0 = wp.cos((wp.abs(v1 + 1.00) * 0.49))
    v1 = 0.04
    tmp = (tmp * (wp.exp(tmp + 0.01) + (tmp + 0.41 - v0 + 0.38)))
    v0 = (((v2 + 0.40 * v1 + 0.08) * wp.cos(v1 + 0.91)) * wp.sin((v0 + 0.60 / v0 + 0.10)))
    data[tid] = v0
